#. Tag: title
#: man-qt6options.7.docbook:57
#, no-c-format
msgid "Options"
msgstr "Võtmed"

#. Tag: para
#: man-qt6options.7.docbook:59
#, no-c-format
msgid "The following options apply to all &Qt; applications:"
msgstr "Järgnevad võtmed kehtivad kõigis &Qt; rakendustes:"

#. Tag: term
#: man-qt6options.7.docbook:64
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<option>-style=</option> <replaceable>style</replaceable> / <option>-style</"
"option> <replaceable>style</replaceable>"
msgstr ""
"<option>-style=</option> <replaceable>stiil</replaceable> / <option>-style</"
"option> <replaceable>stiil</replaceable>"

#. Tag: para
#: man-qt6options.7.docbook:67
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Set the application GUI style. Possible values depend on the system "
#| "configuration. If Qt is compiled with additional styles or has additional "
#| "styles as plugins these will be available to the -style command line "
#| "option."
msgid ""
"Set the application &GUI; style. Possible values depend on the system "
"configuration. If &Qt; is compiled with additional styles or has additional "
"styles as plugins these will be available to the <option>-style</option> "
"command line option."
msgstr ""
"Rakenduse graafilise kasutajaliidese stiili määramine. Võimalikud väärtused "
"sõltuvad süsteemi seadistusest. Kui Qt on kompileeritud lisastiilide "
"toetusega või on tal lisastiilid pluginatena, on ka need käsureavõtmega -"
"style kasutatavad."

#. Tag: term
#: man-qt6options.7.docbook:74
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<option>-stylesheet=</option> <replaceable>stylesheet</replaceable> / "
"<option>-stylesheet</option> <replaceable>stylesheet</replaceable>"
msgstr ""
"<option>-stylesheet=</option> <replaceable>laaditabel</replaceable> / "
"<option>-stylesheet</option> <replaceable>laaditabel</replaceable>"

#. Tag: para
#: man-qt6options.7.docbook:77
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Set the application styleSheet. The value must be a path to a file that "
"contains the Style Sheet."
msgstr ""
"Rakenduse laaditabeli määramine. Väärtus peab olema selle faili asukoht, mis "
"sisaldab laaditabelit."

#. Tag: option
#: man-qt6options.7.docbook:84
#, no-c-format
msgid "-widgetcount"
msgstr "-widgetcount"

#. Tag: para
#: man-qt6options.7.docbook:86
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Print debug message at the end about number of widgets left undestroyed and "
"maximum number of widgets existed at the same time."
msgstr ""
"Lõpus silumisteate näitamine hävitamata jäänud vidinate arvu ning korraga "
"eksisteerinud vidinate maksimaalse arvu kohta."

#. Tag: option
#: man-qt6options.7.docbook:93
#, no-c-format
msgid "-reverse"
msgstr "-reverse"

#. Tag: para
#: man-qt6options.7.docbook:95
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Set the application's layout direction to <methodname>Qt::RightToLeft</"
"methodname>. This option is intended to aid debugging and should not be used "
"in production. The default value is automatically detected from the user's "
"locale (see also <methodname>QLocale::textDirection()</methodname>)."
msgstr ""
"Rakenduse paigutuse suunaks määratakse  <methodname>Qt::RightToLeft</"
"methodname>. See võti on mõeldud silumise parandamiseks ja seda ei peaks "
"kasutama reaalse töö juures. Vaikeväärtus leitakse automaatselt kasutaja "
"lokaadi järgi (vt. ka <methodname>QLocale::textDirection()</methodname>)."

#. Tag: term
#: man-qt6options.7.docbook:104
#, no-c-format
msgid "<option>-qmljsdebugger=</option> <replaceable>port</replaceable>"
msgstr "<option>-qmljsdebugger=</option> <replaceable>port</replaceable>"

#. Tag: para
#: man-qt6options.7.docbook:107
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Activate the QML/JS debugger with a specified port. The value must be of "
"format port:1234[,block], where block is optional and will make the "
"application wait until a debugger connects to it."
msgstr ""
"QML/JS siluri aktiveerimine määratud pordis. Väärtus peab olema kujul "
"port:1234[,block], kus block on lisavõti, mis paneb rakenduse ootama, kuni "
"silur sellega ühenduse loob."

#. Tag: term
#: man-qt6options.7.docbook:114
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<option>-platform</option> <replaceable>platformName[:options]</replaceable>"
msgstr ""
"<option>-platform</option> <replaceable>platvormiNimi[:võtmed]</replaceable>"

